column5: Who would of thought the river would offer 2 for 1 today.LOL  Two steelhead for the price of one pinkie. Then the sale was over.LOL  Dang it was finger knumbing this morning.  First was nicely coloured up,     The second was much fresher. Sorry, had to do the back ground block here guys.
I remember that place! Fast flowing water, a bridge and a dog! Nice fish B.
I remember that place! Fast flowing water, a bridge and a dog! Nice fish B.  I dont dought it. Heck, the dog is probly as old as you.  Keeping it FR as possible here bud.
I know that place with 'snow' all over the place!  It was pretty cold this morning. Already missed 15C we had two days ago ...
Beautifully coloured buck  All dressed up looking for his lady. Sure hope he finds her, as back he went to give it a go.

I know that place with 'snow' all over the place!  It was pretty cold this morning. Already missed 15C we had two days ago ...  It,s always those couple hours of the sunrise that are killer.  After the first fish, I was getting all warm and fuzzy like .
That's waaaay better than fighting the crowds in the malls IMO. Nice Bri!
That's waaaay better than fighting the crowds in the malls IMO. Nice Bri!  Chris, I had no intentions of going to malls boxing day. Today was relaxed out there. Picked up some needed supplies.
